company.description:
The LABE develops research activities, training, calibration, and electrical tests to materials and equipment. It is at the forefront of the industry and is constantly working on new projects. 

The laboratory is ascribed to the Electrical and Electronics Department of the Engineering Faculty of the Universidad Nacional de Colombia, and it has been endowed with technical and human resources unique in the country.
